{
  "texts": [
    "Stacking: The architect's dream, assembles a gallery of base models, each contributing a stroke to the canvas of predictions on a validation set.",
    "The meta-model then conducts a symphonic synthesis, crafting the final decision with the finesse of a virtuoso.",
    "In fraud detection, stacking becomes the curator of diversity, blending decision trees with neural networks to achieve predictive alchemy.",
    "Flexibility is its forte, adapting to the intricacies of data but at the cost of potential complexity.",
    "Designing the stacking architecture demands an artist's touch, and selecting base models is akin to choosing instruments for a grand concerto."
  ]
}